data.description: Lovely ranch home and updated beautifully.   This home has a front porch with room for  outside sitting and as you enter the foyer, the updated kitchen has  beautiful cabinetry, new appliances, flooring and a great bar area overlooking the breakfast area.    Open kitchen looks into the greatroom with a gas fireplace.   There is an oversized deck with space to entertain a large number of guests.   As you enter the back yard, there is a storage building or workshop that could be used even for a child's playhouse.   This home is gracious and inviting.
